        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Air Designation Actions in Areas of Pollutant Transport Act or the ADAAPT Act </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Clean Air Act to revise requirements for certain nonattainment areas, including provisions related to international border areas, marginal areas, and rural transport areas.</p>]]></text>
